    <summary>High level manager used to obtain an instance of an <c><see cref="T:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothAdapter" /></c>
 and to conduct overall Bluetooth Management.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">High level manager used to obtain an instance of an <c><see cref="T:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothAdapter" /></c>
 and to conduct overall Bluetooth Management.
 </para>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">
 Use <c><see cref="M:Android.Content.Context.GetSystemService(System.String)" /></c>
 with <c><see cref="F:Android.Content.Context.BluetoothService" /></c> to create an <c><see cref="T:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothManager" /></c>,
 then call <c><see cref="P:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothManager.Adapter" /></c> to obtain the <c><see cref="T:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothAdapter" /></c>.
 </para>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">
 Alternately, you can just call the static helper
 <c><see cref="P:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothAdapter.DefaultAdapter" /></c>.

 <format type="text/html"><h3>Developer Guides</h3></format></para>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">For more information about using BLUETOOTH, read the
 <format type="text/html"><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/../guide/topics/connectivity/bluetooth.html">Bluetooth</a></format> developer guide.</para>
      <format type="text/html">
        <h5 class="jd-tagtitle">See Also</h5>
      </format>
      <list type="bullet">
        <item>
          <term>
            <c>
              <see cref="M:Android.Content.Context.GetSystemService(System.String)" />
            </c>
          </term>
        </item>
        <item>
          <term>
            <c>
              <see cref="P:Android.Bluetooth.BluetoothAdapter.DefaultAdapter" />
            </c>
          </term>
        </item>
      </list>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">
        <format type="text/html">
          <a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/bluetooth/BluetoothManager.html" target="_blank">[Android Documentation]</a>
        </format>
      </para>
    </remarks>
    <since version="Added in API level 18" />
  </Docs>
